answers.body_markdown:
Use subqueries:

    select (select count(*) from recommendations) / (select count(*) from reservations);

Your query is generating a Cartesian product.  Then each count is counting the number of rows generating.  That count is the same, when you count non-`NULL` columns, so the ratio is `1`.

